#

Beef Tenderloin Tips with Mushrooms

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

quickeasybeefdinner

Description

Tender beef tips sautéed with savory mushrooms in a rich sauce, perfect for a quick dinner.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin tips: 1 pound
  • mushrooms (sliced): 8 ounces
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • beef broth: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley (chopped): for garnish
